[5] Cholera - China
Date: Tue 18 Nov 2014
Source: Xinhua News Agency [edited]
http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/china/2014-11/18/c_133798458.htm


A total of 1448 Chinese died of infectious diseases in October 2014, the National Health and Family Planning Commission said [Tue 18 Nov 2014].

The month saw more than 609 000 cases of infectious disease. 4 reported cases of cholera were reported without deaths.

The statistics do not cover Hong Kong, Macao, or Taiwan.

